                  <p class="card-text text-danger" id="contentArt"></p> <hr>
                  <small id="creatArt">create at: </small> <br> <br>
                  <small id="updatArt">last update: </small> <br><br>
                  <small class="text-info" id="ownerArt"><b class="text-warning">author: </b></small> <br> <br>
